question: The Union Territory of Andaman and Nicobar islands comes under the jurisdiction of a __:
option1: Circuit bench of the Bombay High Court at Port Blair
option2: Circuit bench of the Madras High Court at Port Blair
option3: Circuit bench of the Kolkata High Court at Port Blair
option4: Circuit bench of the Supreme Court at Port Blair
answer: Circuit bench of the Kolkata High Court at Port Blair
